'''B型肝炎疫苗'''（{{lang|en|Hepatitis B vaccine}}），常簡稱'''B肝疫苗'''。是用來預防[[B型肝炎|B型肝炎]]的[[疫苗|疫苗]]<ref name="WHO2009">{{cite journal|title=Hepatitis B vaccines WHO position paper|url=http://www.who.int/wer/2009/wer8440.pdf|date=2 Oct 2009|journal=Weekly epidemiological record|accessdate=2016-03-24|issue=84|volume=40|pages=405–420|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202113955/http://www.who.int/wer/2009/wer8440.pdf|archivedate=2015-12-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一劑建議於出生後的24小時內就注射，要視情況決定之後還須追加第二或第三劑。這包括[[免疫抑制|免疫功能不全]]的患者：例如患有[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]的人，或是[[早產兒|早產兒]]。若是身心健康且有定期接種疫苗，則保護力可高達95% <ref name=WHO2009/>。

高風險族群會建議進行血液檢測以確認疫苗的效用。有免疫功能問題的病人可能有追加注射疫苗的必要，但一般民眾則大多不需要。曾受到[[乙型肝炎病毒|B型肝炎病毒]]感染且尚未有健全免疫力的病患，之後追加施打的疫苗應增加{{le|B型肝炎免疫球蛋白|Hepatitis B immune globulin}}，此疫苗會經由[[肌肉注射|肌肉注射]]的方式接種<ref name=WHO2009/>。

B型肝炎疫苗較少會引發嚴重的副作用，在注射的當下可能會感到些許疼痛。在[[懷孕|懷孕]]或是[[哺乳|哺乳]]期間依舊可以施打疫苗。並沒有證據顯示B肝疫苗和[[格林-巴利症候群|格林-巴利症候群]]有相關性 。現今使用的疫苗是利用[[DNA重組技術|DNA重組技術]]製成的，可以單獨使用或和其他疫苗混合施打<ref name=WHO2009/>。

第一種B肝疫苗是在1981年經美國核准<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=2TMwAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA336|publisher=Newnes|date=2015-11-25|isbn=978-0-12-398375-6|language=en|first=Edward J.|last=Moticka|title=A Historical Perspective on Evidence-Based Immunology|pages=336|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222101535/https://books.google.ca/books?id=2TMwAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA336}}</ref>，1986年另一種更加安全的疫苗获批上市<ref name=WHO2009/>，均由美国微生物学家[[莫里斯·希勒曼|莫里斯·希勒曼]]的团队研发<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Maurice Hilleman: Creator of Vaccines That Changed the World|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7150172/|last=Tulchinsky|first=Theodore H.|date=2018|journal=Case Studies in Public Health|doi=10.1016/B978-0-12-804571-8.00003-2|pages=443–470|pmc=7150172|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117040546/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7150172/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Maurice R Hilleman|url=https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(05)66536-1/abstract|last=Oransky|first=Ivan|date=2005-05-14|journal=The Lancet|issue=9472|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(05)66536-1|volume=365|pages=1682|language=en|issn=0140-6736|pmid=15912596}}</ref>。由于乙肝可引发[[肝癌|肝癌]]，该疫苗也被视为首款抗癌疫苗，获得广泛使用<ref name=":7">{{Cite journal|title=Hepatitis B virus and cancer prevention|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21253790/|last=Chang|first=Mei-Hwei|date=2011|journal=Recent Results in Cancer Research. Fortschritte Der Krebsforschung. Progres Dans Les Recherches Sur Le Cancer|doi=10.1007/978-3-642-10858-7_6|volume=188|pages=75–84|issn=0080-0015|pmid=21253790|access-date=2021-02-13|archive-date=2022-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308083312/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21253790/}}</ref><ref name=":8">{{Cite web|title=Vaccine for Hepatitis B|url=https://www.hepb.org/prevention-and-diagnosis/vaccination/|work=Hepatitis B Foundation|language=en|access-date=2021-02-13|archive-date=2022-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220512042302/https://www.hepb.org/prevention-and-diagnosis/vaccination/}}</ref>。目前此藥名列[[世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單|世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單]]內，同時也是基礎醫療裡很重要的藥物之一<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO Model List of EssentialMedicines|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=22 April 2014|date=October 2013|archivedate=2016-04-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411133939/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年單劑的量販價介於0.58至13.20美元間<ref>{{cite web|title=Vaccine, Hepatitis B|url=http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=HEPBV&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=&desc=Vaccine%2C%20Hepatitis%20B&pack=new&frm=VIAL&rte=INJ&class_code2=19%2E3%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2819%2E3%2E%29Vaccines%3Cbr%3E|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|accessdate=6 December 2015}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，在美國的售價則落在50到100美元的區間內<ref name="Ric2015">{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richart|title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition|date=2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781284057560|page=314}}</ref>。

==疫苗介绍==

=== 免疫机制 ===
疫苗包括一種病毒包膜蛋白，也就是[[乙肝表面抗原|乙肝表面抗原]]（HBsAg），目前是基因工程改造过的（乙肝酵母转基因重组疫苗），可以產生乙肝表面抗原的酵母製造<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rxlist.com/recombivax-drug.htm|title=Hepatitis B Vaccine from Merck|accessdate=2010-05-09|archivedate=2010-04-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100421000459/http://www.rxlist.com/recombivax-drug.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後免疫系統會產生B肝表面蛋白的抗體（anti-HB），抗體及免疫系統的記憶性讓人體可以對抗B型肝炎<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cdc.gov/hepatitis/index.htm|title=CDC Viral Hepatitis|date=2009-07-24|publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|location=Atlanta, Georgia|accessdate=2009-10-22|archivedate=2019-05-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524211846/https://www.cdc.gov/hepatitis/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===接种对象===
若母親為B型肝炎帶原者，嬰兒會在出生24小時內<ref name="cdc.gov.tw">{{Cite web |url=http://www.cdc.gov.tw/professional/info.aspx?treeid=5b0231beb94edffc&nowtreeid=dc132e275cf714e3&tid=D76D08D4B13EB623 |title=衛生福利部疾病管制署專業人士版|accessdate=2016-03-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415230807/http://www.cdc.gov.tw/professional/info.aspx?treeid=5b0231beb94edffc&nowtreeid=dc132e275cf714e3&tid=D76D08D4B13EB623 |archivedate=2016-04-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>接種B型肝炎疫苗，並注射B型肝炎免疫球蛋白（HBIG）<ref name="pmid16371945">{{Cite journal|title=A comprehensive immunization strategy to eliminate transmission of hepatitis B virus infection in the United States: recommendations of the Advisory Committee on Immunization Practices (ACIP) part 1: immunization of infants, children, and adolescents|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16371945|last=Mast|first=Eric E.|last2=Margolis|first2=Harold S.|date=2005-12-23|journal=MMWR. Recommendations and reports: Morbidity and mortality weekly report. Recommendations and reports|issue=RR-16|volume=54|pages=1–31|issn=1545-8601|pmid=16371945|last3=Fiore|first3=Anthony E.|last4=Brink|first4=Edward W.|last5=Goldstein|first5=Susan T.|last6=Wang|first6=Susan A.|last7=Moyer|first7=Linda A.|last8=Bell|first8=Beth P.|last9=Alter|first9=Miriam J.|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511163959/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16371945/}}</ref>，若出生後臨床狀況穩定則越早注射越好<ref name="cdc.gov.tw"/>。現今很多國家注射疫苗以對付B型肝炎。有很多國家B型肝炎感染的機率較高，新生兒接種B型肝炎疫苗不只可以降低感染的風險，也顯著的減少了[[肝癌|肝癌]]的病例。像[[台灣|台灣]]1984年實施的B型肝炎接種計劃也和其兒童肝癌發生率的下降有關<ref name="Chang_1997">{{Cite journal|title=Universal Hepatitis B Vaccination in Taiwan and the Incidence of Hepatocellular Carcinoma in Children|url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/abs/10.1056/NEJM199706263362602|last=Chang|first=Mei-Hwei|last2=Chen|first2=Chien-Jen|date=1997-06-26|journal=New England Journal of Medicine|issue=26|doi=10.1056/NEJM199706263362602|volume=336|pages=1855–1859|language=en|issn=0028-4793|last3=Lai|first3=Mei-Shu|last4=Hsu|first4=Hsu-Mei|last5=Wu|first5=Tzee-Chung|last6=Kong|first6=Man-Shan|last7=Liang|first7=Der-Cherng|last8=Shau|first8=Wen-Yi|last9=Chen|first9=Ding-Shinn}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tccf.org.tw/old/magazine/vol7/8.htm |title=B型肝炎疫苗接種與盛行率之下降 |accessdate=2016-03-25 |archivedate=2017-02-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220215014/http://www.tccf.org.tw/old/magazine/vol7/8.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在英國，會提供B型肝炎疫苗給[[男男性行为者|男男性接觸人群]]，這是性健康檢查的一部分，在愛爾蘭也有類似的措施<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/vaccinations/Pages/hepatitis-b-vaccine.aspx|title=Hepatitis B vaccine|work=www.nhs.uk|accessdate=2016-03-25|archivedate=2017-06-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628184633/http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/vaccinations/Pages/hepatitis-b-vaccine.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。許多地區的所有醫療護理人員及相關實驗室人員，都要接受B型肝炎疫苗接種<ref name="isbn0113225288-c12">{{cite book|author=Joint Committee on Vaccination and Immunisation|title=Immunisation Against Infectious Disease 2006 ("The Green Book")|edition=3rd|chapter=Chapter 12 Immunisation of healthcare and laboratory staff—Hepatitis B|chapterurl=http://www.dh.gov.uk/en/Publichealth/Healthprotection/Immunisation/Greenbook/DH_4097254?IdcService=GET_FILE&dID=115800&Rendition=Web|format=PDF|publisher=Stationery Office|location=Edinburgh|year=2006|pages=468|isbn=0-11-322528-8|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20130107105354/http://www.dh.gov.uk/en/Publichealth/Healthprotection/Immunisation/Greenbook/DH_4097254?IdcService=GET_FILE&dID=115800&Rendition=Web|archivedate=2013-01-07|accessdate=2016-03-25}}</ref>。[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]]建議[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]病患都接受B型肝炎疫苗接種<ref name="pmid22189894">{{Cite journal|title=Use of hepatitis B vaccination for adults with diabetes mellitus: recommendations of the Advisory Committee on Immunization Practices (ACIP)|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22189894|last=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC)|date=2011-12-23|journal=MMWR. Morbidity and mortality weekly report|issue=50|volume=60|pages=1709–1711|issn=1545-861X|pmid=22189894|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512052803/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22189894/}}</ref>。

===疫苗效用===

在首次完成三劑B型肝炎疫苗注射後一到四個月會抽一次血，檢驗B型肝炎病毒表面抗體（anti-hepatitis B surface antigen antibody(anti-Hbs)）的數值是否超過100 mIU/ml<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cdc.gov.tw/professional/knowdisease.aspx?treeid=BEAC9C103DF952C4&nowtreeid=7296679902209942&id=4632148C425C4923&did=656 |title=衛生福利部疾病管制署專業人士版|accessdate=2016-03-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417102358/http://www.cdc.gov.tw/professional/knowdisease.aspx?treeid=BEAC9C103DF952C4&nowtreeid=7296679902209942&id=4632148C425C4923&did=656 |archivedate=2016-04-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>：超過則代表個體對疫苗已經產生適當的免疫反應，通常百分之85到90的人注射完疫苗後會產生反應<ref name="isbn0113225288">{{cite book|author=Joint Committee on Vaccination and Immunisation|pages=468|archivedate=2013-01-07|archiveurl=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20130107105354/http://www.dh.gov.uk/en/Publichealth/Healthprotection/Immunisation/Greenbook/DH_4097254?IdcService=GET_FILE&dID=115800&Rendition=Web|deadurl=yes|isbn=0-11-322528-8|year=2006|title=Immunisation Against Infectious Disease 2006 ("The Green Book")|location=Edinburgh|publisher=Stationery Office|format=PDF|chapterurl=http://www.dh.gov.uk/en/Publichealth/Healthprotection/Immunisation/Greenbook/DH_4097254?IdcService=GET_FILE&dID=115800&Rendition=Web|chapter=Chapter 12 Immunisation of healthcare and laboratory staff—Hepatitis B|edition=3rd|accessdate=2016-03-25}}</ref>。B型肝炎表面抗體數值介在10 到 100 mIU/ml 之間視為對疫苗反應不佳，這些人需要在檢驗出來後再額外注射一劑疫苗，但不需要隔一段時間後再抽血評估<ref name="isbn0113225288" />。

B型肝炎表面抗體數值落在10 mIU/ml以內表示個體對疫苗不反應，這些人在抽血檢查以排除是否過去曾感染B肝或現在正處於感染階段，並且接受額外三劑B型肝炎疫苗注射，注射完成後經一到四個月再抽血檢測B型肝炎表面抗體數值。那些在第二次疫苗注射療程後依舊對疫苗沒有反應的人<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Comparison of the immunogenicity of hepatitis B vaccine administered intradermally and intramuscularly|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/2148433|last=King|first=J. W.|last2=Taylor|first2=E. M.|date=1990-11|journal=Reviews of Infectious Diseases|issue=6|doi=10.1093/clinids/12.6.1035|volume=12|pages=1035–1043|issn=0162-0886|pmid=2148433|last3=Crow|first3=S. D.|last4=White|first4=M. C.|last5=Todd|first5=J. R.|last6=Poe|first6=M. B.|last7=Conrad|first7=S. A.|last8=Gelder|first8=F. B.}}</ref>，可能會對皮內注射、高劑量疫苗<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Immunization with high-dose intradermal recombinant hepatitis B vaccine in healthcare workers who failed to respond to intramuscular vaccination|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7759824|last=Levitz|first=R. E.|last2=Cooper|first2=B. W.|date=1995-02|journal=Infection Control and Hospital Epidemiology|issue=2|doi=10.1086/647062|volume=16|pages=88–91|issn=0899-823X|pmid=7759824|last3=Regan|first3=H. C.|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415130247/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7759824/}}</ref>，或是A型B型肝炎結合疫苗有反應<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Excellent Response Rate to a Double Dose of the Combined Hepatitis A and B Vaccine in Previous Nonresponders to Hepatitis B Vaccine|url=https://academic.oup.com/jid/article-lookup/doi/10.1086/589722|last=Cardell|first=Kristina|last2=Åkerlind|first2=Britt|date=2008-08|journal=The Journal of Infectious Diseases|issue=3|doi=10.1086/589722|volume=198|pages=299–304|language=en|issn=0022-1899|last3=Sällberg|first3=Matti|last4=Frydén|first4=Aril|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207003850/https://academic.oup.com/jid/article-lookup/doi/10.1086/589722}}</ref>，而對疫苗依舊沒有反應的人如果之後暴露到B型肝炎病毒，會需要注射B型肝炎免疫球蛋白（HBIG）<ref name="isbn0113225288" />。

對疫苗反應不佳的人通常是因為以下因素：超過40歲、肥胖、抽菸或酗酒<ref name="pmid8254852">{{Cite journal|title=Hepatitis B vaccine responsiveness in Connecticut public safety personnel|url=http://jama.ama-assn.org/cgi/doi/10.1001/jama.270.24.2931|last=Roome|first=A. J.|date=1993-12-22|journal=JAMA: The Journal of the American Medical Association|issue=24|doi=10.1001/jama.270.24.2931|volume=270|pages=2931–2934}}</ref>，尤其是有嚴重肝病患者<ref name="pmid9316554">{{Cite journal|title=Efficacy of a high and accelerated dose of hepatitis B vaccine in alcoholic patients: a randomized clinical trial|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9316554|last=Rosman|first=A. S.|last2=Basu|first2=P.|date=1997-09|journal=The American Journal of Medicine|issue=3|doi=10.1016/s0002-9343(97)00132-0|volume=103|pages=217–222|issn=0002-9343|pmid=9316554|last3=Galvin|first3=K.|last4=Lieber|first4=C. S.|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225205610/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9316554/}}</ref>。 免疫抑制的病人或接受腎臟透析的病人也可能對疫苗反應較差或需要更大劑量、頻率的疫苗注射<ref name="isbn0113225288" />。至少已有一個研究指出，B型肝炎的疫苗在HIV患者體內較難生效<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Immune responses in patients with HIV infection after vaccination with recombinant Hepatitis B virus vaccine|url=http://bmcinfectdis.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1471-2334-6-65|last=Pasricha|first=Neelam|last2=Datta|first2=Usha|date=2006-12|journal=BMC Infectious Diseases|issue=1|doi=10.1186/1471-2334-6-65|volume=6|pages=65|language=en|issn=1471-2334|pmc=PMC1525180|pmid=16571140|last3=Chawla|first3=Yogesh|last4=Singh|first4=Surjit|last5=Arora|first5=Sunil K|last6=Sud|first6=Archana|last7=Minz|first7=Ranjana W|last8=Saikia|first8=Biman|last9=Singh|first9=Haqeeqat|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308081753/https://bmcinfectdis.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/1471-2334-6-65}}</ref>。

===保護期===

目前認為疫苗只能提供五到七年的免疫保護<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Hepatitis B vaccine: prospects for duration of immunity.|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2590237/|last=Krugman|first=S.|last2=Davidson|first2=M.|date=1987|journal=The Yale Journal of Biology and Medicine|issue=4|volume=60|pages=333–339|issn=0044-0086|pmc=2590237|pmid=3660859|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308104853/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2590237/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Duration of hepatitis B immunity in low risk children receiving hepatitis B vaccinations from birth|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15247604|last=Petersen|first=Kenneth M.|last2=Bulkow|first2=Lisa R.|date=2004-07|journal=The Pediatric Infectious Disease Journal|issue=7|doi=10.1097/01.inf.0000130952.96259.fd|volume=23|pages=650–655|issn=0891-3668|pmid=15247604|last3=McMahon|first3=Brian J.|last4=Zanis|first4=Carolyn|last5=Getty|first5=Marilyn|last6=Peters|first6=Helen|last7=Parkinson|first7=Alan J.|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507045850/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15247604/}}</ref>，但隨後發現人體[[免疫記憶功能|免疫記憶功能]]會發展出長期免疫。長期免疫會長久維持而不受體內抗體減少的影響，因此在疫苗成功建立對B型肝炎病毒免疫功能的個體中，終生不需要再做抗體數值追蹤及補打疫苗<ref name="pmid17291637">{{Cite journal|title=Long-term immunogenicity of hepatitis B vaccination in a cohort of Italian healthy adolescents|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17291637|last=Gabbuti|first=Andrea|last2=Romanò|first2=Luisa|date=2007-04-20|journal=Vaccine|issue=16|doi=10.1016/j.vaccine.2007.01.045|volume=25|pages=3129–3132|issn=0264-410X|pmid=17291637|last3=Blanc|first3=Pierluigi|last4=Meacci|first4=Francesca|last5=Amendola|first5=Antonella|last6=Mele|first6=Alfonso|last7=Mazzotta|first7=Francesco|last8=Zanetti|first8=Alessandro R.|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228162314/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17291637/}}</ref><ref name="pmid10683019">{{Cite journal|title=Are booster immunisations needed for lifelong hepatitis B immunity? European Consensus Group on Hepatitis B Immunity|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10683019|date=2000-02-12|journal=Lancet (London, England)|issue=9203|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(99)07239-6|volume=355|pages=561–565|issn=0140-6736|pmid=10683019|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224144430/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10683019/}}</ref>。在長期實驗中，那些施打疫苗一開始即有適當抗體數量的個體，疫苗保護力至少維持25年<ref name="pmid17298912">{{Cite journal|title=A review of the long-term protection after hepatitis A and B vaccination|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17298912|last=Van Damme|first=Pierre|last2=Van Herck|first2=Koen|date=2007-03|journal=Travel Medicine and Infectious Disease|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.tmaid.2006.04.004|volume=5|pages=79–84|issn=1477-8939|pmid=17298912|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225024407/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17298912/}}</ref>。英國的指導方針建議對於需要持續保護力的人群，例如醫藥衛生工作者，至少每五年施打一劑疫苗<ref name="isbn0113225288" />。

===副作用===

近來有多項研究聚焦在觀察成人施打重組B型肝炎疫苗與[[多發性硬化症|多發性硬化症]]（MS）間的關連。大部分已發表的科學研究多數都不認為B型肝炎疫苗和脫髓鞘疾病（如：多發性硬化症）有任何關係<ref name="CDCFAQ">{{cite web|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vaccinesafety/Vaccines/multiplesclerosis_and_hep_b.html|title=CDC - Hepatitis B and Multiple Sclerosis ( MS) - Vaccine Safety|work=cdc.gov|accessdate=2016-03-25|archivedate=2017-12-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222074702/https://www.cdc.gov/vaccinesafety/Vaccines/multiplesclerosis_and_hep_b.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。只有一篇發表於2004年的研究顯示，在注射疫苗後的三年內，發病的機率有顯著提昇<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Recombinant hepatitis B vaccine and the risk of multiple sclerosis: A prospective study|url=http://www.neurology.org/cgi/doi/10.1212/01.WNL.0000138433.61870.82|last=Hernan|first=M. A.|last2=Jick|first2=S. S.|date=2004-09-14|journal=Neurology|issue=5|doi=10.1212/01.WNL.0000138433.61870.82|volume=63|pages=838–842|language=en|issn=0028-3878|last3=Olek|first3=M. J.|last4=Jick|first4=H.}}</ref>。這當中有部分研究所採用的方法是飽受批評的。而這樣的爭議也誤導大眾對於注射B肝疫苗的想法，在少數幾個國家，孩童中有施打B肝疫苗的人數依舊偏低。2006年的另一篇研究得出的結論是，並沒有任何證據證明B肝疫苗和嬰兒猝死症、慢性疲勞症候群或是多發性硬化症之間有任何關係<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Protective efficacy, immunotherapeutic potential, and safety of hepatitis B vaccines|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16372285|last=Zuckerman|first=Jane N.|date=2006-02|journal=Journal of Medical Virology|issue=2|doi=10.1002/jmv.20524|volume=78|pages=169–177|issn=0146-6615|pmid=16372285|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224144016/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16372285/}}</ref>。於2007年公佈的研究認為，B肝疫苗並不會增加幼童時期罹患初期多發性硬化症的風險<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Hepatitis B vaccination and the risk of childhood-onset multiple sclerosis|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18056563|last=Mikaeloff|first=Yann|last2=Caridade|first2=Guillaume|date=2007-12|journal=Archives of Pediatrics & Adolescent Medicine|issue=12|doi=10.1001/archpedi.161.12.1176|volume=161|pages=1176–1182|issn=1538-3628|pmid=18056563|last3=Rossier|first3=Mélanie|last4=Suissa|first4=Samy|last5=Tardieu|first5=Marc|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506162410/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18056563/}}</ref>。2009年有一項研究針對B型肝炎疫苗和中樞神經炎症性[[脱髓鞘病|脱髓鞘病]]間的關係進行研究，發現B型肝炎疫苗其實是相對安全的，真正有疑慮的是安在時（Engerix B vaccine）疫苗似乎會增加男嬰罹患中樞神經炎症性脱髓鞘病的風險，且高達三倍之多<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.neurology.org/cgi/content/abstract/72/10/873|title=Hepatitis B vaccine and the risk of CNS inflammatory demyelination in childhood|year=2009|publisher=Neurology|accessdate=2016-03-25|archivedate=2010-10-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101029003510/http://www.neurology.org/cgi/content/abstract/72/10/873|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但該研究也被批評，所用的研究方法尚有待商榷<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.who.int/vaccine_safety/committee/topics/hepatitisb/multiple_sclerosis/oct_2008/en/|title=Global Advisory Committee on Vaccine Safety: response to the paper (in press) by Y. Mikaeloff and colleagues in Neurology entitled "Hepatitis B vaccine and the risk of CNS inflammatory demyelination in childhood"|year=2008|publisher=World Health Organization|accessdate=2016-03-25|archivedate=2016-03-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322173220/http://www.who.int/vaccine_safety/committee/topics/hepatitisb/multiple_sclerosis/oct_2008/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

